TEXT.TITLE: HUGH KEITH <HKME.O> COMPLETES ACQUISITION
TEXT.BODY: Hugh Keith Mobile Enterprises Ltd said it completed the acquisition of 59 acres of land adjacent to its mobile home park near Stuart, Fla., for 850,000 dlrs in cash and notes. Reuter
